The paper discusses the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the limitations of CNNs in handling relational concepts, which is a topic of interest in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions attention mechanisms, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL) and neural networks (cs.NE).
